kle.com/ |title=Afewerk Tekle |publisher=Maitreafewerktekle.com |date= |accessdate= 3 August 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ethioembassy.org.uk/news/press%20releases/Afewerk%20Tekle%20Awarded%20Honour.htm |title=Afewerk Tekle Awarded Honour |publisher=Ethioembassy.org.uk |date=29 July 2004 |accessdate=3 August 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218102129/http://www.ethioembassy.org.uk/news/press%20releases/Afewerk%20Tekle%20Awarded%20Honour.htm |archive-date=18 February 2012 |dead-url=yes |df=dmy-all }}</ref> * [[Abel Tilahun]], visual artist * [[Elizabeth Habte Wold]], mixed-media artist * [[Zerihun Yetmgeta]]<ref name="ethiopianmillennium.com">[http://www.ethiopianmillennium.com/arts.html ] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328143958/http://www.ethiopianmillennium.com/arts.html |date=28 March 2010 }}</ref> {{div col end}}
